\widowctrl\hyphauto

{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Reaper Scripts for Game Audio\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 This is a collection of scripts that I wrote for Reaper. Feel free to use them and share them with the game audio community. Have fun guys!\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 Sws, RealmGui, and js_ReaScriptApI extensions need to be installed for the scripts to run.\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 \outlinelevel0 \b \fs36 Installation\par}
{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li0 \fi0 You can install these scripts using ReaPack by navigating to: Extensions > ReaPack > Import Repositories Copy and Paste this link https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Afrodiaq/Afrodiaq-Reascripts/refs/heads/master/index.xml\par}
}
